016/j.pharmthera.2005.01.001 }}</ref><ref name="FMO3-Primary" /> [[butyrate-CoA ligase|XM-ligase]],<ref name="Benzoic1" /> and [[glycine N-acyltransferase|ACGNAT]]<ref name="Benzoic2" />
